From a single specimen anatomically examined from Qingcheng Houshan (
Figs 3-4
). Right ommatophoral retractor crossed vagina and penis. Inner wall of the penis finely reticulated (
Fig. 4A
), produced by the perpendicular projections of the slender longitudinal folds. Inner wall of vagina with widelyspaced, sometimes converging longitudinal folds (
Fig. 4B
).
